&quot;:418244,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://howmuch.net/articles/us-exports-imports-trade-balance">HowMuch.net</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>由于南亚和东南亚的快速增长，即使我们继续与中国脱钩，该地区对美国经济的重要性<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-next-phase-of-globalization-is">也只会增加</a>。</p><p>与此同时，中东作为贸易伙伴绝对很小。特别是，美国根本不依赖中东石油。由于水力压裂，我们成为<a href="https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-poised-become-net-exporter-crude-oil-2023-2022-12-19/">原油净出口国</a>。沙特阿拉伯、阿联酋和科威特可能会被哥斯拉吃掉，而我们的炼油厂将继续运转。 （顺便说一句，拜登领导下的美国石油产量<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/08/09/business/oil-production-biden-trump/index.html">刚刚创下新纪录</a>。）</p><p>现在，我们的一些盟友，比如日本和韩国，确实仍然购买了大量中东石油。如果中东石油供应出现严重中断，全球石油价格将大幅上涨，为美国石油生产商带来意外之财，但也会损害美国其他类型的企业。但<a href="https://about.bnef.com/blog/electric-cars-have-dented-fuel-demand-by-2040-theyll-slash-it/">由于电动汽车的兴起</a>，石油对全球经济的重要性日益降低。预计石油总消耗量很快就会持平。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg" width="655" height="398" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:398,&quot;width&quot;:655,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:65391,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：国际能源署</figcaption></figure></div><p>中东冲突导致石油价格相对于电动汽车和其他替代品的价格上涨，只会加速这一趋势。</p><p>因此，中东对美国的经济重要性正在迅速下降，尽管亚洲继续变得更加重要。将美国从亚洲经济超级集群中剔除将严重损害我们国家的繁荣，而我们实际上不再需要从中东得到太多东西。</p><p>因此，美国应该继续尽可能减少在中东的存在。这并不意味着我们应该完全退出。在极端情况下，明智、有针对性地运用美国力量可以防止经常困扰该地区的一些灾难——保护叙利亚库尔德人免遭种族灭绝，限制以色列对巴勒斯坦人的暴行，或者帮助以色列保护自己免受伊朗及其盟友的大规模破坏。代理。但这些行动应该始终以最少的力量、金钱和注意力来完成，并且始终着眼于再次撤军。</p><p>与此同时，在亚洲，美国应该加强我们的防御力量和与其他国家的接触。我们要加快向台湾、日本、越南、印度、菲律宾等国提供防御性武器，不断建设、加强和扩大四方机制等多边组织。我们需要通过<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/japan-wants-u-s-back-in-the-tpp-it-will-likely-have-to-wait-11618570801">重新加入修改后的TPP</a>以及在亚洲建立一个由其他经济协议组成的密集网络来重新进行经济接触。总的来说，我们只需要对该地区给予大量关注，确保我们的盟友、准盟友和潜在盟友知道我们将长期驻守该地区，而不会突然撤退，陷入一些愚蠢的事情中。中东冲突。</p><p>即使面对以色列-加沙战争和其他分裂、情绪化、引人注目的冲突，拜登政府及其继任者也需要大量的纪律和大量的解释才能继续将重心转向亚洲。但无论如何我们都必须这样做。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/asia-is-much-more-important-to-us?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/asia-is-much-more-important-to-us?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p>; 
