 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>同时，收入与其他发展指标（如教育和健康指标）密切相关。</p><p>但是，按照今天的收入对国家进行分类并不能说明这里的整个故事，因为它不会随着时间的流逝而显示。例如，如果您查看构成“全球南部”的五个主要世界银行地区，例如东亚和太平洋，拉丁美洲和加勒比海，中东和北非，南亚，南亚和撒哈拉以南非洲 - 您&#39; LL看到他们有四个截然不同的轨迹： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4aa8fdac-f5d6-4cc5-b05e-64ae7f26893e_1020x729.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4aa8fdac-f5d6-4cc5-b05e-64ae7f26893e_1020x729.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4aa8fdac-f5d6-4cc5-b05e-64ae7f26893e_1020x729.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4aa8fdac-f5d6-4cc5-b05e-64ae7f26893e_1020x729.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4aa8fdac-f5d6-4cc5-b05e-64ae7f26893e_1020x729.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4aa8fdac-f5d6-4cc5-b05e-64ae7f26893e_1020x729.jpeg" width="1020" height="729" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4aa8fdac-f5d6-4cc5-b05e-64ae7f26