l,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:796,&quot;width&quot;:1194,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:229488,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbea10940-8b67-4f78-9a13-814e01219cdf_1194x796.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbea10940-8b67-4f78-9a13-814e01219cdf_1194x796.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbea10940-8b67-4f78-9a13-814e01219cdf_1194x796.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbea10940-8b67-4f78-9a13-814e01219cdf_1194x796.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"> <a href="https://unsplash.com/@nate_dumlao?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Nathan Dumlao</a>的照片在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/man-in-white-shirt-carrying-girl-in-gray-shirt-Wr3comVZJxU?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上</figcaption></figure></div><p>最近，美国人习惯于阅读一堆可怕的新闻 - 战争，通货膨胀，政治动荡等。在这件事要担心的事情中，好消息往往会在雷达下飞行。因此，您友好的邻里经济博客作者确实是在这里将其带到雷达<em>之上</em>……或任何隐喻。无论如何，这是一些好消息。</p><p>一周前，美联储和财政部从《消费者财务调查》（SCF）中<a href="https://www.federalreserve.gov/econres/scfindex.htm">发布了2022年的数据</a>，这是他们每三年进行一次大型调查，他们向家庭询问其财务状况。家庭调查很重要，因为它们允许我们计算中<em>位数</em>之类的东西 - 如果您想知道国民收入或财富分配中间的家庭如何进行，则需要与大量家庭交谈以找出该分配好像。家庭调查的一个缺点是，他们需要很长时间才能完成（这就是为什么SCF仅每三年出现一次），因此他们不会为您提供最新信息。另一个缺点是，您必须非常谨慎地调查哪些家庭，才能获得代表性样本。但是，即使有这些局限性，调查数据也大大提供了信息。</p><p>基本上，2022年的数字（您可以在<a href="https://www.federalreserve.gov/publications/files/scf23.pdf">美联储的报告</a>中进行了总结）讲述了一个令人鼓舞的故事。简而言之：</p><ul><li><p>自大流行以来，美国人的财富就在上升。</p></li><li><p>加剧的增加，分销的底部的人比顶部人数的人数比人数多。</p></li><li><p>不平等现成，包括种族不平等，教育不平等，城乡不平等，整体财富不平等。</p></li><li><p>债务要小得多。</p></li><li><p>关于收入和财富，甚至还有一些令人惊讶的好消息。</p></li></ul><p>换句话说，涨潮正在抬起所有船。我知道很难相信，在您在媒体上看到的所有厄运和忧郁，但数字不言而喻。就这样，您就知道，我在这篇文章中给出的所有数字均已调整为通货膨胀，因此不必担心。</p><h4>首先，好消息</h4><p>最大的好消息是，典型的美国家庭在2019年至2022年之间获得了约37％的丰富： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg" width="528" height="555" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:555,&quot;width&quot;:528,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:57737,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6439e8a3-168b-4c9c-bcfd-0d04b8ec83e9_528x555.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.federalreserve.gov/publications/files/scf23.pdf">FRB</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>深蓝色条增加的事实超过浅蓝色条，这意味着不等式下降了。在2010年代后期也是如此，但是那几年的财富增加了较慢。因此，2020年代初期是一个富裕。</p><p> （请注意，SCF对“家庭”的定义实际上非常接近人口普查局对“家庭”的定义，这是您通常在这些统计数据中引用的。因此，尽管我通常不会互换使用这些术语，但我在这里我会.)</p><p>这意味着三年来美国家庭中位家庭的财富增加了约51,800美元。不错！中位家庭净资产现在约为192,900美元。这<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_wealth_per_adult">比瑞士信贷的预测</a>高得多，将使美国在世界上排名第六或第七。</p><p>更令人惊讶的是，即使是增加的增长 - 它确实是全面的。这只是我选择的几个小组，但是报告中的所有小组的数字都是正面的。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg" width="1265" height="649" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:649,&quot;width&quot;:1265,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:107020,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F74210983-0996-4f41-83f3-abe47de18603_1265x649.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.federalreserve.gov/publications/files/scf23.pdf">FRB</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>在过去三年中，每个群体不仅变得更加丰富，而且不平等在多个线路上都会降低 - 年龄差距，种族差距，教育差距，城乡差距和整体不平等。</p><p>我<em>没有</em>在图表上包括的两个小组是由不到35岁的人领导的家庭，而财富分配的25％的人。我不包括它们的原因是因为它们太大了 - 增加分别为143％和900％。</p><p> <em>900％？</em>这怎么可能呢？答案是，分销的下半部分几乎没有净财富一开始。在2019年，最底层的25％的典型家庭的净资产仅为400美元，在2022年增加到3500美元。这仍然是非常低的财富。但是请记住，这是一个<em>净</em>数字 - 在美国没有太多财富的人通常会有很多<em>债务</em>，这取消了他们拥有的资产。</p><p>最底层25％的财富如此之多的重要原因是美国人正在慢慢摆脱债务。自2010年以来，债务收入比率一直稳步下降： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fafd2cd80-a4fb-4cf6-9a27-6817fd67e0cf_1084x562.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fafd2cd80-a4fb-4cf6-9a27-6817fd67e0cf_1084x562.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fafd2cd80-a4fb-4cf6-9a27-6817fd67e0cf_1084x562.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fafd2cd80-a4fb-4cf6-9a27-6817fd67e0cf_1084x562.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:ste